name: Add Google Sheets rows for new pages accepted in your Qwilr
description: Every time a new page is accepted in your Qwilr, Make will automatically add a row in your Google Sheets sheet. Here's the [sheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1e0tEoR60_N2C9n4XyPtVCC1xsiOcRn-95h9hwr209bo/edit?usp=sharing) used in this scenario.
